WEBVTT

00:05.200 --> 00:07.800
WOMAN:
I hope you don't mind
decaf, Father.

00:07.800 --> 00:10.200
It's all we had
in the cupboard.

00:10.400 --> 00:12.900
A night this cold, I'll
take whatever I can get.

00:13.900 --> 00:16.300
Colleen's upstairs
when you're ready.

