00:25.300 --> 00:26.200
Colleen?

00:30.500 --> 00:33.100
Colleen, it's me.

00:38.000 --> 00:39.100
It's all right!

00:39.500 --> 00:41.900
Colleen, it's only me.

00:42.400 --> 00:44.500
I'm here to pray
with you.

00:46.300 --> 00:48.200
F-Father?

00:52.700 --> 00:55.200
Oh, Father,
I'm so sorry.

00:55.200 --> 00:57.400
I-I didn't realize...

00:57.400 --> 00:58.300
It's all right,
my child.

00:58.300 --> 01:02.000
No, no, no, no,
it isn't all right.

01:02.200 --> 01:03.900
You're His emissary,
and I-I tried to hurt you.

01:03.900 --> 01:05.200
I-I need to make it up to you.

01:05.200 --> 01:08.800
I need to make it up to Him.

01:08.800 --> 01:09.900
I can hurt myself!

01:09.900 --> 01:11.700
Please don't, Colleen.

01:12.100 --> 01:15.500
He doesn't want that,
and neither do I.

01:23.900 --> 01:26.500
Michael, Michael
buys them for me.

01:26.600 --> 01:27.700
Mother doesn't know.

01:27.800 --> 01:29.200
She doesn't like me to have candy,

01:29.200 --> 01:30.800
 because
she thinks the sugar excites me,

01:30.800 --> 01:32.800
but Michael knows
they make me happy.

01:32.800 --> 01:34.400
He let's me have two a day.

01:34.400 --> 01:36.600
He counts them every day
to make sure that's all I have,

01:36.600 --> 01:38.700
but I've only had one today,
Father,

01:38.700 --> 01:40.500
and I want you
to have the other.

01:48.500 --> 01:49.300
Hail Mary full of grace,

01:49.300 --> 01:50.200
the Lord is with thee.

01:50.200 --> 01:51.600
Blessed art thou among women

01:51.600 --> 01:53.500
and blessed is the fruit
of thy womb, Jesus.

01:53.500 --> 01:56.100
Holy Mary, Mother of God,
pray for our sinners now

01:56.100 --> 01:57.700
and at the hour of our death.

01:57.700 --> 01:58.600
Amen.

01:58.600 --> 02:00.100
Hail Mary, full of grace...

